Overlaps: meQTLs and eQTMs

dex/veh/delta meQTLs

cpgs <- list(meqtl = meqtl.veh.df$CpG_ID %>%
    unique(), eqtm.fdr = eqtm.veh.fdr.df$CpG_ID %>%
    unique(), eqtm.nom = eqtm.veh.nom.df$CpG_ID %>%
    unique())

upset(fromList(cpgs), sets = c("meqtl", "eqtm.fdr", "eqtm.nom"), nsets = 3, nintersects = 20, mainbar.y.label = "Number of intersections, veh CpGs",
    text.scale = 1, keep.order = T, sets.bar.color = c("#0072B2", "#009E73", "#E69F00"), order.by = "freq")

meQTLs groups based on fold change direction

parallel.fc.grp.veh.dex.cpg <- names(meqtl.parallel.fc.grp.veh.dex.gr@anno)

cpgs <- list(parallel_fc_dex_veh = unique(parallel.fc.grp.veh.dex.cpg), eqtm_all_fdr = eqtm.all.fdr.df$CpG_ID %>%
    unique(), eqtm_all_nom = eqtm.all.nom.df$CpG_ID %>%
    unique())

upset(fromList(cpgs), sets = c("parallel_fc_dex_veh", "eqtm_all_fdr", "eqtm_all_nom"), nsets = 3, nintersects = NA,
    mainbar.y.label = "Number of intersections, CpGs \n dex + veh with parallel FC", text.scale = 1,
    keep.order = T, sets.bar.color = c("#0072B2", "#009E73", "#E69F00"), order.by = "freq")

cpgs <- list(parallel_fc_delta = unique(parallel.fc.grp.delta.cpg), eqtm_all_fdr = eqtm.all.fdr.df$CpG_ID %>%
    unique(), eqtm_all_nom = eqtm.all.nom.df$CpG_ID %>%
    unique())

upset(fromList(cpgs), sets = c("parallel_fc_delta", "eqtm_all_fdr", "eqtm_all_nom"), nsets = 3, nintersects = 20,
    mainbar.y.label = "Number of intersections, CpGs \n delta with parallel FC", text.scale = 1, keep.order = T,
    sets.bar.color = c("#0072B2", "#009E73", "#E69F00"), order.by = "freq", empty.intersections = "on")

cpgs <- list(opposite_fc = unique(opposite.fc.grp.cpg), eqtm_all_fdr = eqtm.all.fdr.df$CpG_ID %>%
    unique(), eqtm_all_nom = eqtm.all.nom.df$CpG_ID %>%
    unique())

upset(fromList(cpgs), sets = c("opposite_fc", "eqtm_all_fdr", "eqtm_all_nom"), nsets = 3, nintersects = 20,
    mainbar.y.label = "Number of intersections, CpGs \n opposite FC", text.scale = 1, keep.order = T,
    sets.bar.color = c("#0072B2", "#009E73", "#E69F00"), order.by = "freq", empty.intersections = "on")
